### Hello endpoint — returns a simple greeting
GET http://localhost:8080/api/hello
Accept: application/json

### List all todos (sorted by createdAt desc)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos
Accept: application/json

### Create a new todo
POST http://localhost:8080/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy milk"
}

### Get one todo by id (replace {id} with a value from the list response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos/{id}
Accept: application/json

### Update a todo (replace {id})
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/todos/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy oat milk",
  "completed": true
}

### Delete a todo (replace {id})
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/todos/{id}
